    "### Predict next token\n",
    "- Cross-entropy loss\n",
    "$$\n",
    "L = -\\sum y \\log(\\hat{y})\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "> Teacher forcing: use true tokens as input during training\n",
    "\n",
    "    - Target is the next token after input in the sequence\n",
